<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1441372>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5–16. Dissomphalus, ♂. 5–8. D. boitata sp. nov.. 5. Head, dorsal view. 6. Aedeagus, dorsal view. 7. Aedeagus, ventral view. 8. Paramere, anterolateral view. 9–11. D. boto sp. nov.. 9. Head, dorsal view. 10. Genitalia, dorsal view. 11. Genitalia, ventral view. 12–16. D. curupira sp. nov.. 12. Head, dorsal view. 13. Tergal process, dorsal view. 14. Genitalia, dorsal view. 15. Genitalia, ventral view. 16. Apical lobes of aedeagal dorsal body, dorsal view. Scales-bar: 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1441372/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1441374>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17–29. Dissomphalus, ♂. 17–20. D. iara sp. nov.. 17. Head, dorsal view. 18. Tergal process, dorsal view. 19. Genitalia, dorsal view. 20. Genitalia, ventral view. 21–24. D. saci sp. nov.. 21. Head, dorsal view. 22. Tergal process, lateral view. 23. Genitalia, dorsal view. 24. Genitalia, ventral view. 25–29. D. irupe sp. nov.. 25. Head, dorsal view. 26. Spine in gena, lateral view. 27. Tergal process, dorsal view. 28. Genitalia, dorsal view. 29. Genitalia, ventral view. Scales-bar: 100 µm." ;
